<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Andreea & Bogdan | 17 Octombrie 2026</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

:root{
  --black:#111;
  --cream:#f6f3ee;
  --gold:#b89b72;
}

*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  background:var(--cream);
  color:var(--black);
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
  height:100vh;
  position:relative;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  text-align:center;
  color:white;
  overflow:hidden;
}

.hero img{
  position:absolute;
  width:100%;
  height:100%;
  object-fit:cover;
  filter:brightness(0.55);
  transform:scale(1.05);
}

.overlay{
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.65));
}

.hero-content{
  position:relative;
  z-index:2;
  max-width:800px;
  padding:20px;
}

.ab{
  font-size:3rem;
  letter-spacing:8px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

h1{
  font-size:3.5rem;
  font-weight:500;
}

.date{
  margin-top:10px;
  letter-spacing:4px;
  font-size:1rem;
  color:#e7d7b8;
}

.hero p{
  margin-top:25px;
  font-size:1.2rem;
  line-height:1.6;
}

/* SECTION */
section{
  padding:90px 20px;
  text-align:center;
}

.container{
  max-width:1000px;
  margin:auto;
}

/* COUNTDOWN */
.countdown{
  background:white;
}

.counter{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:20px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  margin-top:30px;
}

.box{
  background:var(--cream);
  padding:25px;
  width:120px;
  border-radius:10px;
}

.box span{
  font-size:2rem;
  font-weight:bold;
}

/* PROGRAM */
.card{
  background:white;
  padding:30px;
  margin:15px;
  border-radius:12px;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

/* BUTTON */
.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  margin-top:15px;
  padding:10px 20px;
  border:1px solid var(--gold);
  color:var(--gold);
  text-decoration:none;
}

/* CONFIRM */
.confirm{
  background:#111;
  color:white;
}

.phone{
  margin-top:20px;
  font-size:1.2rem;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
  background:#0d0d0d;
  color:white;
  padding:80px 20px;
  text-align:center;
}

footer h2{
  font-size:2.5rem;
  letter-spacing:2px;
}

footer p{
  margin-top:10px;
  color:#bbb;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">

<img src="WhatsApp Image 2026-06-16 at 22.57.58.jpeg">

<div class="overlay"></div>

<div class="hero-content">

<div class="ab">A | B</div>

<h1>Andreea & Bogdan</h1>

<div class="date">17 OCTOMBRIE 2026</div>

<p>
Unele povești se scriu în timp.  
A noastră ne-a purtat prin zâmbete, provocări și visuri.  
Astăzi vă invităm să fiți alături de noi.
</p>

</div>

</div>

<!-- COUNTDOWN -->
<section class="countdown">
<h2>Numărătoarea inversă</h2>

<div class="container">

<div class="counter">
<div class="box"><span id="days">0</span><br>Zile</div>
<div class="box"><span id="hours">0</span><br>Ore</div>
<div class="box"><span id="minutes">0</span><br>Minute</div>
<div class="box"><span id="seconds">0</span><br>Secunde</div>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<!-- PROGRAM -->
<section>
<h2>Programul zilei</h2>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<h3>Ceremonia religioasă</h3>
<p>13:45 - Sf. Ursula, Sibiu</p>
<a class="btn" href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/HpbPHdZDZt3Yvgf98?g_st=ac">Google Maps</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Recepția</h3>
<p>16:00 - Versailles Weddings & Events</p>
<a class="btn" href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/NbdNcMfB191yJSf19?g_st=ac">Google Maps</a>
</div>

<p style="margin-top:30px;">
Vă rugăm să ajungeți la ora 16:00 la locația petrecerii.
</p>

</div>
</section>

<!-- CONFIRM -->
<section class="confirm">
<h2>Confirmare participare</h2>

<p>Vă rugăm să confirmați până la 1 octombrie 2026</p>

<div class="phone">Andreea: 0749401444</div>
<div class="phone">Bogdan: 0752634381</div>

</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
<h2>A | B</h2>
<p>Andreea & Bogdan — 17 Octombrie 2026</p>
<p>Vă așteptăm cu drag</p>
</footer>

<script>

const wedding = new Date("Oct 17, 2026 13:45:00").getTime();

setInterval(()=>{

const now = new Date().getTime();
const d = wedding - now;

document.getElementById("days").innerText = Math.floor(d/(1000*60*60*24));
document.getElementById("hours").innerText = Math.floor((d%(1000*60*60*24))/(1000*60*60));
document.getElementById("minutes").innerText = Math.floor((d%(1000*60*60))/(1000*60));
document.getElementById("seconds").innerText = Math.floor((d%(1000*60))/1000);

},1000);

</script>

</body>
</html>
